extends layout

block content
    .page.js-page
      // One Page Sidebar
      .one-page-sidebar
        // One Page Sidebar Header
        .one-page-sidebar-header
          // One Page Logo
          .one-page-logo
            // Logo Image
            a.logo-image(href='/friends')
              img(src='/images/logo2.png')
            br
            a.logo-image(href='/friends')
              img(src='/images/friend.png')
            // End of Logo Image
          // End of One Page Logo
          // One Page Meta
          // End of One Page Meta
        // End of One Page Sidebar Header
        // One Page Nav
        .one-page-nav-wrapper.js-custom-scrollbar
          ul.one-page-nav.js-one-page-nav.js-menu-vertical(data-prepend-to='.js-prepend-mobile-menu')
            li.is-active
              a(href='#apply_job')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-envelope
                | Apply a Job
            li
              a(href='#Current_Jobs')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-black-tie
                | Current Jobs
            li
              a(href='#Search_network_jobs\
              ')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-search
                | Search network jobs
            li
              a(href='#Search_public_jobs\
              ')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-search-plus
                | Search public jobs
            li
              a(href='#Connections\
              ')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-connectdevelop
                | Connections
            li
              a(href='#Social_Media_share\
              ')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-share
                | Social Media share
            li
              a(href='#Upload_Resume\
              ')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-upload
                | Upload Resume
            li
              a(href='#Apply_a_Job\
              ')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-edit
                | Apply a Job
        // End of One Page Nav
        // One Page Sidebar Footer
        footer.one-page-sidebar-footer
          | All Rights Reserved.
          a(href='http://www.masymbol.com/', target='_blank') Masymbol Technologies
          |  Pvt Ltd © 2016
        // End of One Page Sidebar Footer
      // End of One Page Sidebar
      // One Page Content
      .one-page-content
        // Header
        header.header.large.header-one-page.js-header-fixed
          .container-fluid.container-spaced
            .row
              .col-md-3.col-sm-6.col-xs-5
                .visible-sm-block.visible-xs-block
                  // Logo Image
                  a.logo-image(href='/')
                    img.img-responsive(src='https://s3.amazonaws.com/skilledtree-public/logo.png', alt='logo')
                  // End of Logo Image
              .col-md-12.col-sm-6.col-xs-7
                // Menu
                nav.right.helper
                  ul.menu.sf-menu.js-menu
                    li
                      a(href='/friends')
                        i.fa.fa-home.fa-lg
                    li
                      a(href='/friends/introduction')
                        | Introduction
                    li
                      a.active(href='/friends/current_openings')
                        | Current Openings
                    li
                      a(href='/friends/job_tweets') Job Tweets
                    li
                      a(href='/friends/share_resumes') Share your resume
                    li
                      a(href='/friends/resumes') Resumes
                    li
                      a(href='/friends/my_profile') My Profile
                    li
                      a(href='/friends/header') Header
                // End of Menu
        // End of Header
        #content
          .container-fluid.container-spaced
            .col-md-12
              #apply_job.category-info.helper.pt0
                h1 Apply a Job
                p.category-content
                  | You can apply to numerous amount of jobs which are suitable to your SkillSets. You can apply to the same job on behalf of your friends by uploading their resumes in it. Your resume status will be notified by GCM, SMS / via Emails. You can track your application status and your friends too.
              // Category Info
              #Current_Jobs.category-info.helper.pt0
                h1
                  | Current Jobs
                  // Fragment Identifier
                  // End of Fragment Identifier
                p.category-content
                  | In order to get more jobs,  you need to connect with your friends as much as you can. So whenever their company posted any jobs, you will be getting those jobs in your ‘Current Openings’ page.
            .col-md-12
              // Category Info
              #Search_network_jobs.category-info.helper.pt0
                h1
                  | Search network jobs
                  // Fragment Identifier
                  // End of Fragment Identifier
                p.category-content
                  | You can search any of the jobs which are posted by the members in your network whom you have connected with.
            .col-md-12
              // Category Info
              #Search_public_jobs.category-info.helper.pt0
                h1
                  | Search public jobs
                  // Fragment Identifier
                  // End of Fragment Identifier
                p.category-content
                  | Not only inside your network, You can search the public open jobs in SkilledTree which is available on the top left Sidebar.
            .col-md-12
              // Category Info
              #Connections.category-info.helper.pt0
                h1
                  | Connections
                  // Fragment Identifier
                  // End of Fragment Identifier
                p.category-content
                  | Total number of friends you have connected with.
            .col-md-12
              // Category Info
              #Social_Media_share.category-info.helper.pt0
                h1
                  | Social Media share
                  // Fragment Identifier
                  // End of Fragment Identifier
                p.category-content
                  | You can share this job to any of your social media account such as Facebook, Twitter, LinkedIn, Google+ and Pinterest. Your friends too can apply for those jobs you have shared.
            .col-md-12
              // Category Info
              #Upload_Resume.category-info.helper.pt0
                h1
                  | Upload Resume
                  // Fragment Identifier
                  // End of Fragment Identifier
                p.category-content
                  | In order to apply to the job on behalf of your friend, you can apply it by uploading their resume. Automatically, SkilledTree will be created for them. Login credentials will be sent to their Email / SMS will be sent.
            .col-md-12
              // Category Info
              #Apply_a_Job.category-info.helper.pt0
                h1
                  | Apply a Job
                  // Fragment Identifier
                  // End of Fragment Identifier
                p.category-content
                  | You can apply to the any job by clicking on the Job Title. It will redirect to the new tab along with the Job description.
            .row
              .col-md-8
                img(src='/images/F1.png', width='100%')
      // End of One Page Content
